<h1>Congrats!</h1>

<p>Thanks to our generous donor - Matteo Ricci - you can put your credit card away as we prepare your Covid Care Package to be shipped.</p>
<br>
<h2>You sent your package to:</h2>

<div class = recipient-info>
<!--- receipient name -->
<%= @package.recipient_name %> at
<!--- receipient address -->
<%= @package.recipient_address %>
<!--- receipient message -->
</div>

<p class = "msg">Your Message to <%="#{@package.recipient_name}"%>:</p>
<%= @package.recipient_message %>

<h4 class = "packageitems">Which will include:</h4>
<!--- confirm items--->
<% @package.items.each do |item| %>
    <ul>
        <li><%= item.name %></li>
    </ul>
<% end %>

<div class = "linktohome">
    <%= link_to "Return to Account Home", user_path(@package.user)%>
</div>